                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<p>Here you will find the most favored Group of Interest formatted articles on the site. Voting is restricted to site members, to avoid vandalism.</p>
<p>GoI Formats are stories written within the Foundation universe from the perspective of an organization that is not the SCP Foundation. <a href="/groups-of-interest">Click here to see all Groups of Interest.</a></p>
